title: Courtney Barnett Wins Big at Australias Independent Music Awards
text:
Courtney Barnett Wins Big at Australia's Independent Music Awards 
Billboard Biz Friday 23rd October, 2015 
. 
Few independent music aficionados would have expected anything less than a dominant night from Barnett. The rising star scooped a pair of prizes...
